    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Best Noise Canceling Headphones for Work in 2026</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated June 2026 · Evaluated 6+ models</div>

      <p>Open offices, coffee shops, and home environments with kids and pets all destroy focus. Active noise cancellation (ANC) used to cost $300 or more, locked behind the Sony and Bose flagship tier. In 2026, the gap between budget and flagship has narrowed enough that most knowledge workers do not need to spend flagship money to get silence.</p>

      <nav class="toc" aria-label="Table of contents">
        <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
        <ol>
          <li><a href="#how-we-tested">How We Evaluated</a></li>
          <li><a href="#ranking-methodology">Ranking Methodology</a></li>
          <li><a href="#quick-comparison">Quick Comparison</a></li>
          <li><a href="#best-overall">Best Overall</a></li>
          <li><a href="#best-budget">Best Budget</a></li>
